       | nfo:                                                         |
       | The joint-first golf game to get a release for the GameCube  |
       | in the UK - along with Tiger Woods 2003 - Ace Golf offers the|
       | usual array of game modes, allowing for both short, quickfire|
       | matches and the more intense, longer tournaments. To be more |
       | precise, there's Tournament, Stroke, Match, and Short Course |
       | modes available, as well as a collection of fun mini games,  |
       | such as 'Nearest Pin', which is played on a nine-hole,       |
       | par-three course.                                            |
